Daikon is due to be a CLI for ElasticSearch to make some of the basic admin
tasks associated with ElasticSearch a little easier than using curl... you know
for us lazy folks.

Functions:

    * Working with Indexes
        * Create Indexes
        * Delete Indexes

    * Working with Clusters
        * Health View
        * State View
        * Shutdown Clusters

    * Working with Nodes
        * Stats
        * Shutdown
